<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Biofouling Management Plan — {{vessel.name}}</title>
  <style>
    /* ================================================================
       BIOFOULING MANAGEMENT PLAN (BFMP) REPORT TEMPLATE
       Professional A4 Print-Ready Document
       Following IMO Biofouling Guidelines (MEPC.207(62))
       ================================================================ */

    /* ---- Reset & Base Typography ---- */
    * {
      font-family: 'Calibri', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      background: white;
      display: block;
    }

    body {
      max-width: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0;
      color: #1e293b;
      font-size: 11pt;
      line-height: 1.55;
      background: white;
    }

    /* ---- Page Structure ---- */
    .page {
      page-break-after: always;
      size: A4;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 20mm 17mm 15mm 17mm;
      min-height: 297mm;
      position: relative;
    }

    .page:last-child {
      page-break-after: auto;
    }

    .pageLast {
      size: A4;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 20mm 17mm 15mm 17mm;
      min-height: 297mm;
      position: relative;
      page-break-after: auto;
    }

    /* ---- Page Header & Footer (Print) ---- */
    .page-header,
    .page-header-space {
      height: 100px;
    }

    .page-footer,
    .page-footer-space {
      height: 70px;
    }

    .page-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0mm;
      left: 0;
      width: 210mm;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      padding: 8mm 17mm 0 17mm;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .header-table {
      width: 100%;
      table-layout: fixed;
      border: none;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .header-table td {
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: middle;
      border: none;
      padding: 0;
      background: none;
    }

    .header-table td:first-child {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .header-table td:last-child {
      text-align: right;
    }

    .page-footer {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 210mm;
      padding: 0 17mm 8mm 17mm;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .page-footer-inner {
      border-top: 2px solid #365F91;
      padding-top: 6px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .page-footer-inner .footer-left {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .page-footer-inner .footer-center {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #365F91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 7pt;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .page-footer-inner .footer-right {
      text-align: right;
    }

    #confidential {
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      word-spacing: 2px;
      color: #FF0000;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-style: normal;
      font-variant: normal;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ---- Heading Hierarchy ---- */
    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #365F91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #365F91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #365F91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: left;
      margin: 22px 0 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #365F91;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    h4 {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #365F91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: left;
      margin: 18px 0 8px 0;
    }

    h5 {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #365F91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: left;
      margin: 12px 0 6px 0;
    }

    h6 {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #365F91;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: left;
      margin: 8px 0 4px 0;
    }

    p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-size: 11pt;
    }

    .subtitle {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #475569;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    /* ---- Cover Page ---- */
    .cover {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 25mm;
    }

    .cover-org {
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .cover-org h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #64748b;
      text-transform: none;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .cover-title {
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .cover-title h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #365F91;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .cover-vessel {
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .cover-vessel h2 {
      font-size: 26px;
      color: #1e293b;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .cover-imo {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cover-image-placeholder {
      width: 80%;
      max-width: 420px;
      height: 180px;
      border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-style: italic;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: #f8fafc;
    }

    .cover-image-placeholder img {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .cover-meta {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 11pt;
      color: #334155;
      width: 70%;
    }

    .cover-meta table {
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .cover-meta td {
      padding: 6px 14px;
      text-align: left;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .cover-meta td:first-child {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #365F91;
      background: #f0f4f8;
      width: 40%;
    }

    .cover-footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 2px solid #365F91;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }

    /* ---- Table Styles ---- */
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 8px 0 16px 0;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }

    th {
      background-color: #365F91;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border: 1px solid #365F91;
      font-size: 10pt;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    td {
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      vertical-align: top;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }

    tr {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    tr:nth-child(even) td {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
    }

    .label-cell {
      background-color: #e8edf4;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #334155;
      width: 35%;
    }

    .label-cell-narrow {
      background-color: #e8edf4;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #334155;
      width: 25%;
    }

    /* Key-value table */
    .kv-table {
      margin: 8px 0 16px 0;
    }

    .kv-table td {
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
    }

    /* Data table with dense layout */
    .data-table th {
      font-size: 9pt;
      padding: 5px 8px;
    }

    .data-table td {
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      padding: 4px 8px;
    }

    /* ---- Risk Badges ---- */
    .risk-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 3px 12px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10pt;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .risk-low {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: #166534;
      padding: 3px 12px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }

    .risk-medium {
      background: #fef9c3;
      color: #854d0e;
      padding: 3px 12px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }

    .risk-high {
      background: #fed7aa;
      color: #9a3412;
      padding: 3px 12px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }

    .risk-veryhigh {
      background: #fecaca;
      color: #991b1b;
      padding: 3px 12px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 10pt;
    }

    .risk-overall {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 18px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13pt;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* ---- Condition Badges ---- */
    .condition-good {
      color: #166534;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .condition-fair {
      color: #854d0e;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .condition-poor {
      color: #9a3412;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ---- Section Intro ---- */
    .section-intro {
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 10.5pt;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .section-note {
      background: #f0f4f8;
      border-left: 3px solid #365F91;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      margin: 12px 0;
      font-size: 10pt;
      color: #334155;
    }

    /* ---- Empty State ---- */
    .empty-state {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-style: italic;
      padding: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px dashed #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* ---- Footer Line (in-page) ---- */
    .footer-line {
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      padding-top: 8px;
      font-size: 8.5pt;
      color: #94a3b8;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .page-number {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 12mm;
      right: 17mm;
      font-size: 8.5pt;
      color: #94a3b8;
    }

    /* ---- Table of Contents ---- */
    .toc-section {
      margin: 6px 0;
      font-size: 11pt;
      line-height: 2;
    }

    .toc-section a {
      color: #365F91;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .toc-section a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .toc-main {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 11.5pt;
    }

    .toc-sub {
      margin-left: 22px;
      font-size: 10.5pt;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    /* ---- Signoff ---- */
    .signoff-block {
      margin: 20px 0;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .signoff-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .signoff-table td {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .signoff-label {
      background: #e8edf4;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #334155;
      width: 30%;
    }

    .signature-line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
      height: 40px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .signature-date-line {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e293b;
      width: 200px;
      height: 30px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    /* ---- Disclaimer ---- */
    .disclaimer {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: #64748b;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ---- Distribution List ---- */
    .distribution-table td {
      font-size: 10pt;
    }

    /* ---- Image / Photo Styles ---- */
    .image-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      min-height: 160px;
      border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      font-style: italic;
      margin: 12px auto;
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .image-placeholder img {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: 400px;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .photo-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .photo-grid .photo-item {
      flex: 1 1 45%;
      min-width: 200px;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .photo-grid .photo-item img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .photo-caption {
      font-size: 8.5pt;
      color: #64748b;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 4px;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* ---- Risk Matrix ---- */
    .risk-matrix-table td {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 8px 12px;
    }

    .risk-matrix-table .matrix-low {
      background: #dcfce7;
      color: #166534;
    }

    .risk-matrix-table .matrix-medium {
      background: #fef9c3;
      color: #854d0e;
    }

    .risk-matrix-table .matrix-high {
      background: #fed7aa;
      color: #9a3412;
    }

    .risk-matrix-table .matrix-veryhigh {
      background: #fecaca;
      color: #991b1b;
    }

    /* ---- Divider ---- */
    .section-divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }

    /* ---- Utility ---- */
    .text-center { text-align: center; }
    .text-left { text-align: left; }
    .text-right { text-align: right; }
    .text-bold { font-weight: 700; }
    .text-muted { color: #94a3b8; }
    .text-small { font-size: 9pt; }
    .mt-0 { margin-top: 0; }
    .mt-10 { margin-top: 10px; }
    .mt-20 { margin-top: 20px; }
    .mb-0 { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .mb-10 { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .mb-20 { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .no-border td { border: none; }
    .full-width { width: 100%; }

    section {
      page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    /* ================================================================
       @page — Print Page Setup
       ================================================================ */
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 17mm;
    }

    /* ================================================================
       @media screen — Preview Mode (A4 cards on grey background)
       ================================================================ */
    @media screen {
      html {
        background: #e8ecf1 !important;
      }

      body {
        background: transparent !important;
        max-width: none !important;
        width: auto !important;
        padding: 40px 20px !important;
        margin: 0 !important;
        height: auto !important;
        overflow-y: auto !important;
      }

      .page-header {
        display: none !important;
      }

      .page-footer {
        display: none !important;
      }

      .page-header-space,
      .page-footer-space {
        height: 0 !important;
        display: none !important;
      }

      .page,
      .pageLast {
        width: 210mm !important;
        min-height: 297mm !important;
        margin: 0 auto 40px auto !important;
        padding: 20mm 17mm !important;
        background: white !important;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12), 0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;
        border-radius: 2px !important;
        box-sizing: border-box !important;
        position: relative !important;
        page-break-after: unset !important;
      }
    }

    /* ================================================================
       @media print — Print Overrides
       ================================================================ */
    @media print {
      thead {
        display: table-header-group;
      }

      tfoot {
        display: table-footer-group;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        max-width: none;
        position: relative;
        height: 297mm;
        width: 210mm;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .page {
        page-break-after: always;
        padding: 0;
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .pageLast {
        page-break-after: auto;
        padding: 0;
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .no-print {
        display: none !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- ============================================================
       FIXED PAGE HEADER (for print)
       ============================================================ -->
  <div class="page-header">
    <table class="header-table">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <!-- Logo placeholder: organisation logo renders here -->
          {{#if organisation.name}}
            <span style="font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 600; color: #365F91;">{{organisation.name}}</span>
          {{/if}}
        </td>
        <td>
          <p id="confidential">CONFIDENTIAL</p>
        </td>
        <td>
          <span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #64748b;">BFMP &mdash; Rev. {{planInformation.revision}}</span>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ============================================================
       FIXED PAGE FOOTER (for print)
       ============================================================ -->
  <div class="page-footer">
    <div class="page-footer-inner">
      <span class="footer-left">{{#if organisation.name}}{{organisation.name}}{{/if}}</span>
      <span class="footer-center">Biofouling Management Plan</span>
      <span class="footer-right">Rev. {{planInformation.revision}} &mdash; {{planInformation.date}}</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Wrapper table for repeating header/footer in print -->
  <table style="width:100%; border:none; margin:0; padding:0;">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <td style="border:none; padding:0;">
          <div class="page-header-space"></div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tfoot>
      <tr>
        <td style="border:none; padding:0;">
          <div class="page-footer-space"></div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tfoot>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td style="border:none; padding:0;">


  <!-- ============================================================
       PAGE 1: COVER PAGE
       ============================================================ -->
  <div class="page cover">

    <div class="cover-org">
      {{#if organisation.name}}
        <h2 style="font-size: 18px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 2px;">{{organisation.name}}</h2>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    <div style="width: 80%; border-top: 3px solid #365F91; margin: 10px auto;"></div>

    <div class="cover-title">
      <h1 style="font-size: 30px; margin-bottom: 4px;">Biofouling</h1>
      <h1 style="font-size: 30px; margin-top: 0;">Management Plan</h1>
    </div>

    <div style="width: 40%; border-bottom: 3px solid #365F91; margin: 10px auto;"></div>

    <div class="cover-vessel">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 24px; color: #1e293b;">{{vessel.name}}</h2>
    </div>

    {{#if vessel.imoNumber}}
      <p class="cover-imo">IMO {{vessel.imoNumber}}</p>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="cover-image-placeholder">
      Vessel Photograph / Company Logo
    </div>

    <div class="cover-meta">
      <table>
        {{#if planInformation.reference}}
        <tr>
          <td>Plan Reference</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.reference}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
        <tr>
          <td>Revision</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.revision}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{#if planInformation.date}}
        <tr>
          <td>Date</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.date}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if planInformation.preparedBy}}
        <tr>
          <td>Prepared By</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.preparedBy}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if planInformation.approvedBy}}
        <tr>
          <td>Approved By</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.approvedBy}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if planInformation.approvalDate}}
        <tr>
          <td>Approval Date</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.approvalDate}}</td>
        </tr>
        {{/if}}
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="cover-footer">
      <p>Biofouling Management Plan in accordance with IMO Guidelines (MEPC.207(62))</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 4px;">Generated: {{generatedAt}}</p>
    </div>

  </div>


  <!-- ============================================================
       PAGE 2: DOCUMENT STATUS / REVISION TABLE
       ============================================================ -->
  <div class="page">

    <h3>Document Status &amp; Revision History</h3>

    <p class="section-intro">
      This document is a controlled copy of the Biofouling Management Plan. Any amendments must be approved by the
      designated authority and recorded in the revision history below.
    </p>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="width: 12%;">Revision</th>
          <th style="width: 15%;">Date</th>
          <th style="width: 20%;">Prepared By</th>
          <th style="width: 20%;">Approved By</th>
          <th>Description</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td style="text-align: center;">{{planInformation.revision}}</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.date}}</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.preparedBy}}</td>
          <td>{{planInformation.approvedBy}}</td>
          <td>Current revision</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4 style="margin-top: 30px;">Distribution List</h4>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="width: 8%;">No.</th>
          <th style="width: 20%;">Copy Type</th>
          <th>Holder / Location</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td style="text-align: center;">1</td>
          <td>Controlled</td>
          <td>Vessel &mdash; Master's Office</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="text-align: center;">2</td>
          <td>Controlled</td>
          <td>{{#if company.name}}{{company.name}} &mdash; {{/if}}Shore Office</td>
        </tr>
